うと", "するヤツは"]}, {"box": [348, 751, 367, 854], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["すみません"]}, {"box": [84, 751, 146, 875], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["僕そんな", "つもりじゃ．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-123.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [636, 390, 681, 480], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["もしやと", "思ったけど"]}, {"box": [307, 395, 363, 467], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["相田．．", "だっけ？"]}, {"box": [593, 653, 690, 757], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["な．．．なに", "やってんの？", "そんなカッコ"]}, {"box": [393, 537, 446, 596], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["やっぱ", "碇か．．．"]}, {"box": [365, 652, 425, 781], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["戦争ー", "“ごっこ”かな？"]}, {"box": [68, 743, 121, 799], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["へんな", "ヤツ．．．"]}, {"box": [367, 852, 416, 906], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ひとり", "で？"]}, {"box": [351, 953, 374, 994], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ああ"]}, {"box": [237, 851, 316, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["碇こそなに", "やってんのさ", "こんなとこで"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-124.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [659, 36, 672, 127], "vertical": true, "font_size": 13.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [428, 58, 440, 132], "vertical": true, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [65, 63, 113, 139], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["メシ．．．", "食うか？"]}, {"box": [642, 561, 666, 606], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ほら"]}, {"box": [487, 575, 532, 682], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["トウジのやつ", "心配してたよ"]}, {"box": [267, 578, 345, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["きのう碇が", "学校に", "来なかったから"]}, {"box": [107, 566, 231, 706], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おとといの", "戦闘のあとさ", "おまえずいぶんと", "まいってた", "みたいだったし"]}, {"box": [107, 565, 232, 709], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おとといの戦闘のあとさおまえずいぶんとまいってたみたいだったし"]}, {"box": [48, 723, 121, 859], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ーでも", "わりと元気そうで", "安心したよ"]}, {"box": [646, 870, 686, 947], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["サンキュー"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-125.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [538, 57, 553, 150], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [417, 61, 497, 152], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ーー碇は", "大変そうだ", "けどさ"]}, {"box": [140, 32, 222, 127], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["俺すっげー", "うらやま", "しいよ"]}, {"box": [549, 423, 675, 563], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんてったって", "あんなかっこいい", "ロボット操縦", "できるんだ", "もんな"]}, {"box": [93, 519, 230, 684], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["俺も", "一度でいいから", "思いのままに", "エヴァンゲリオンを", "操ってみたいよ"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-126.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [620, 48, 666, 139], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["僕もそんな", "ふうに．．．"]}, {"box": [545, 44, 593, 171], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["思えたら", "いいんだけどな"]}, {"box": [515, 413, 582, 500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["思え", "ないの？"]}, {"box": [575, 646, 644, 773], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["碇シンジ君", "だね？"]}, {"box": [366, 525, 413, 581], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まあね"]}, {"box": [475, 867, 646, 942], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["その時は、", "そういうわけで、"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-127.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [680, 22, 700, 66], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["な．．．"]}, {"box": [606, 29, 660, 181], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["なんだよ", "あんたたちは！？"]}, {"box": [611, 305, 702, 432], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ネルフ", "保安諜報部の", "者だ"]}, {"box": [92, 294, 334, 366], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ナピぽゆぺポポぺ"]}, {"box": [633, 707, 697, 851], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["保安条例第８項", "の適用により"]}, {"box": [128, 820, 192, 943], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["君を本部まで", "連行する"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-128.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [505, 29, 529, 116], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いいね？"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-129.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [408, 28, 433, 110], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["結局僕は．．"]}, {"box": [278, 183, 349, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ここに戻って", "来るしか", "ないのか．．"]}, {"box": [197, 72, 237, 200], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ミサトさん", "怒ってるだろうな"]}, {"box": [76, 217, 132, 297], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["．．．", "なんだかわかんな"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-130.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [350, 72, 370, 110], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ．．．"]}, {"box": [66, 143, 87, 231], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ただいま．．"]}, {"box": [421, 314, 442, 395], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["おかえり"]}, {"box": [300, 295, 372, 368], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["どう？", "家出した", "気分は．．"]}, {"box": [60, 294, 168, 418], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["２日間", "ほっつき歩いて", "少しは気が", "晴れたかしら？"]}, {"box": [638, 539, 662, 667], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["すみません．．．"]}, {"box": [314, 545, 370, 649], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ひとつだけ", "聞くわ"]}, {"box": [511, 890, 534, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["でした"]}, {"box": [129, 686, 218, 931], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あなたはこれから先", "エヴァのパイロットとして", "やってく気があるの？"]}, {"box": [45, 806, 98, 888], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それとも", "ないの？"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-131.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [646, 361, 697, 432], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["やる気も", "なにも"]}, {"box": [83, 361, 208, 579], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["乗りたくないって", "言ったって", "しょーがないじゃ", "ないですか"]}, {"box": [604, 529, 623, 631], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["言ったでしょ"]}, {"box": [475, 522, 575, 662], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["僕は最初から", "乗りたくて", "乗ってるワケじゃ", "ないって．．"]}, {"box": [596, 730, 700, 853], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["だって", "パイロットは", "僕しかいないん", "でしょ"]}, {"box": [125, 834, 233, 973], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["僕が", "乗らなきゃ", "みんな困るんじゃ", "ないですか？"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-132.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [562, 70, 622, 242], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["みんながやれって", "言うから僕は"]}, {"box": [42, 143, 167, 335], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["人のことなんか", "関係ないわ", "あなたがどうかって", "聞いてるのよ！"]}, {"box": [320, 387, 350, 473], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["シンジ君"]}, {"box": [511, 806, 598, 970], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あなたが", "乗りたくないなら", "それでいいの．．"]}, {"box": [53, 853, 138, 958], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["おじさんの", "所へ", "戻りなさい"]}], "img_path": "EVA2-133.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [374, 69, 447, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["このままじゃ", "あなたのために", "ならない"]}, {"box": [88, 73, 163, 147], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["死ぬのを", "早める", "だけだわ"]}, {"box": [423, 312, 445, 376], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["それに"]}, {"box": [87, 309, 205, 497], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あなたみたいに", "中途半端な気持ちで", "乗られるのは", "こっちも迷惑なのよ"]}, {"box": [415, 651, 516, 775], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["そりゃ．．．", "パイロットが", "いな